<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-10 px-4">
  <div class="mb-8">
    <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium">
      ← Back to Demo
    </a>
  </div>

  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-8">
    This Privacy Policy explains how Mycowriter collects, uses, and shares information.
    It also explains your privacy rights, including California and Colorado privacy options.
  </p>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700">
      <li>Basic request data (IP address, user agent, referrer, timestamps).</li>
      <li>Analytics and advertising identifiers (cookies or similar technologies) if ads are enabled.</li>
      <li>Account information if you register (email, display name, and related profile data).</li>
      <li>Voluntary contact information if you email us.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">How We Use Information</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700">
      <li>Operate and secure the site and user accounts.</li>
      <li>Provide and improve features, including autocomplete services.</li>
      <li>Measure site performance and content engagement.</li>
      <li>Serve advertising on public pages (AdSense), if enabled.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Advertising and Cookies</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">
      We may use Google AdSense to display ads on public pages. Google and its partners may use
      cookies or similar technologies to provide, measure, and improve ads, including interest-based ads.
    </p>
    <p class="text-gray-700">
      If you opt out below, we disable AdSense on this site for your browser. We also honor Global Privacy Control (GPC)
      signals when provided by your browser.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">California and Colorado Privacy Rights</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">
      If you are a resident of California or Colorado, you may have the right to opt out of targeted advertising
      and the sale or sharing of personal information for advertising purposes. You can exercise this right below.
    </p>
    <p class="text-gray-700">
      You can also contact us to request access, correction, or deletion of personal information we maintain.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-10">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Opt Out of Targeted Advertising</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
      Current status:
      <strong><%= @adsense_opted_out ? "Opted out" : "Not opted out" %></strong>
    </p>
    <div class="flex gap-4">
      <%= button_to "Do Not Sell or Share My Personal Information (Opt Out)", privacy_opt_out_path, method: :post, class: "bg-red-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded" %>
      <%= button_to "Opt Back In to Ads", privacy_opt_in_path, method: :post, class: "bg-gray-200 text-gray-800 px-4 py-2 rounded" %>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Contact</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700">
      Email: <a href="mailto:will@mrdbid.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">will@mrdbid.com</a>
    </p>
  </section>

  <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
    Last updated: 2026-03-14
  </p>
</div>
